Let's start with the cereal because it seems
the simplest but it turns out to be one of

00:00:16.030 --> 00:00:22.020
the most surprising. The simple explanation
goes like this. So, I showed you cereal is

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:28.960
magnetic. I have ground up all of this cereal
into a very fine powder. Let us see what is

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:33.960
in it. I'm going to take these strong magnets
and run them over the cereal powder and see

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:40.690
if anything is attracted to them. Look how
the cereal actually sticks to the magnet.

00:00:40.690 --> 00:00:47.180
And it's because there's pieces of iron in
this cereal. They've been added because iron

00:00:47.180 --> 00:00:51.680
is something we need, it's an essential nutrient
